[This fast moving disease seems to be one step ahead by adapting to increasing pressures. We can only hope at this point that it is not necessarily a more resistant strain to our attempts to rid ourselves of this virus.

The research thus for on the length of time the virus remains active in the water may be longer than thought and this may be a key to finding a way to kill it. - Mod.TG]
